<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            font-family: 'Google Sans', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .main-card {
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dadce0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .logo img {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 0;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e8f0fe;
            color: #1a73e8;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #202124;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .message {
            color: #3c4043;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .otp-box {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #1a73e8;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            padding: 18px 24px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e8eaed;
        }

        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #dadce0;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            color: #70757a;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #1a73e8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .security-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #5f6368;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: left;
            border-left: 4px solid #dadce0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="main-card">
             <div class="logo">
                <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #202124;">NexBuy</span>
            </div>

            <div class="badge">Security Alert</div>
            <h1>Seller Account Recovery</h1>

            <div class="message">
                Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,<br><br>
                We received a request to reset your password for the NexBuy Seller Portal. Please use the following code to verify your identity and set a new password:
            </div>

            <div class="otp-box">
                <%= otp %>
            </div>

            <div class="message" style="margin-top: 25px;">
                This code will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong>.
            </div>

            <div class="security-note">
                <strong>Didn't make this request?</strong><br>
                If you didn't ask to reset your seller account password, your account is still safe. No further action is required, but we recommend checking your recent store activity for peace of mind.
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <div class="message" style="font-size: 12px; color: #70757a; margin-bottom: 0;">
                Securely sent by NexBuy Merchant Services.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 NexBuy Business | Merchant Security Division</p>
            <p>
                <a href="#">Seller Help Center</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Security Privacy</a> &bull;
                <a href="mailto:helmi.abouchakra@gmail.com">Contact Merchant Support</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>